
Monitors multiple APIs organized in a matrix structure to detect drift, latency spikes, and outage clusters.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIDriftMatrix - Endpoint Health Drift Tracker

APIDriftMatrix surfaces hidden shifts in API response time and tracks downtime patterns across a large network.

## Features
- Matrix-configurable endpoints  
- Drift + burst alerts  
- CSV / JSON reporting  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_APIDriftMatrix.git
cd 25_APIDriftMatrix
python monitor.py
